quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  14,11,"Nulaa…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen maakani …ďe: \"[Ko goonga], men wonaali si wanaa …ďanndinke yeru mon, kono Alla no mo∆ī∆īoo e Mo O muuyi e jeyaa…ďe Makko …ďen. Laatanaaki men nde men addana on hujja, si wanaa e duŇčayee Alla. Ko e Alla gom…óim…ďe …ďen fawotoo"
  14,12,"Ko ha…óata men nde fawotoo e Alla, gom…óii O fewnii men (e) laawi amen? Ma men mu√Ī√Īo e kon ko lorroton men. Ko e Alla gom…óim…ďe …ďen fawotoo"
  14,13,"∆Āen yeddu…ďe (kadi) wi'ani Nulaa…ďe mun …ďen: \"Ma men yaltin on ka leydi amen, maa rutto…óon e diina amen\". Joomi ma…ď…ďe wahayini e ma…ď…ďe: \"Ma men halku too√Īu…ďe …ďen"
  14,14,"Ma Men ho…ónu on e leydi ndin …ďaawo ma…ď…ďe. ∆äum ko wonannde on hulu…óo daroyagol yeeso Am, o huli kammbaa Am on"
  14,15,∆Āe …óa…ď…ďi uddital. Sooyi kala dunndaranke ∆īaggu…óo
  14,16,"Jahannama no yesso makko, himo yarniree ndiyam mbordi ∆īii∆īiiri"
  14,17,"himo woo…ďa …óam, e …óe…ďataa …ďennugol …óam. Maayde nden ardana mo e kala nokku, kono o wonaali maayoowo. Hara no yeeso makko lepte sattu…óe"
  14,18,"Ko woni sifa …ďen yeddu…ďe Joomi mun, kuu…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen, ko wano ndoondi ndi henndu tii…ói e mun, e √Īalaande wippoore. ∆Āe hettoytaa huunde e ko …ďe faggitinoo. Ko …óum woni majjere won…ó…óunde"
